 {"title": "Agent-assisted dialing for executive access", "detail": "Live operators navigate phone trees, handle gatekeepers, and connect your reps only when the target decision-maker is on the line. For enterprise teams trying to reach VPs and C-suite executives, this human layer gets through where automated detection can't. It's expensive but effective for high-value conversations."},
 {"title": "Mature caller ID management", "detail": "Koncert actively monitors caller ID reputation, rotates numbers flagged as spam, and assigns local presence numbers matching prospect area codes. Poor caller ID management can cut answer rates by 50% or more. Koncert treats this as a core feature, not an afterthought. Their experience (formerly ConnectAndSell) gives them deep expertise here."},
 {"title": "Enterprise-grade compliance and security", "detail": "TCPA compliance features, DNC list management, and calling hour restrictions are built into the platform. For regulated industries or companies calling consumers (B2B2C scenarios), Koncert's compliance tools reduce legal risk. SOC 2 certification and enterprise security features satisfy IT procurement requirements."},
