 {"title": "Complex setup and configuration", "detail": "Supporting four dialing modes means four sets of configurations, workflows, and best practices to learn. Implementation typically requires Koncert's professional services team and takes 2-4 weeks for full deployment. Teams wanting to start dialing on day one will find the ramp frustrating."},
 {"title": "Enterprise-focused pricing excludes smaller teams", "detail": "Koncert's pricing is custom and oriented toward enterprise buyers. Minimum seat requirements and annual contracts are standard. Teams under 10 reps may find the investment disproportionate to their needs, especially if they only use one or two dialing modes."},
